name: ExtensionSubstanceDefinition_Name
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.SubstanceDefinition.name` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `SubstanceDefinition.name` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `SubstanceDefinition.name` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`SubstanceDefinition.name` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `SubstanceDefinition.name` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `SubstanceDefinition.name` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `SubstanceSpecification.name` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `SubstanceDefinition.name` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `SubstanceSpecification.name`, but has no comparisons.
